citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T22:55:34.000Z","msg":"連登仔：正廢老，樓價仲穩過銀行定期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，銀行執笠樓價唔會跌，樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33f49836dc433617fdd890784bf61a7280c42b4","tid":771381,"uid":88252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T23:00:45.000Z","msg":"想當年梁錦松買架車慳左十幾萬登記稅比人追擊到落台<br />\n<br />\n十幾年後大家都見怪不怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a54c6071a8dbc0a92ea874263eff3b96c26b39","tid":771381,"uid":12241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T23:56:59.000Z","msg":"早就同d淡淡講過 政府官員大把幾十層樓幾萬呎地<br />\n佢地冇可能會比樓市跌 佢地退左休一樣要食飯一樣係貪錢<br />\n記住 林鄭都係打份工 你估真係為民請命 唔好咁on9"},{"pid":"791a028c863d8e3615eb5dd294dee030cd3d3b66","tid":771381,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40f54da5a248c00e3cebacb0dd268806911d964","tid":771381,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T02:13:03.000Z","msg":"呢條19 又做鬼祟野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T23:59:10.000Z","msg":"打999有咩用呢<br />\n呢班殖民地打手有特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}